      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$i - Explanatory text</strong> <div class="description">Text, such as <em>Example under [...]</em> and <em>Note under [...]</em>, that
                              indicates the use of the heading in the authority record for the heading referred
                              to in subfield $a.
         </div>
