      <h3>CONTENT DESIGNATOR HISTORY</h3>
      <div class="font_small"><em>Indicator 1 - Print constant [OBSOLETE, 1997] [CAN/MARC only]</em><br>Values defined were: 0 (No print constant required), 1 (Example under/Exemple sous),
                        2 (Note under/Note sous), 3 (Example under reference from/Exemple sous le renvoi
                     de)<br>
                     <br><em>$a - Subject heading or subdivision term [REDEFINED, 1991] [USMARC only]</em></div>
